data.title: Lane College partners with the University of Tennessee to expand nursing opportunities
data.meta_description: In collaboration with the University of Tennessee Health Science Center, Lane College students will now have a direct pathway to continue their education in nursing once receiving their associate’s degree from Lane, a partnership that was announced on Jan. 18.
